Let's proceed with the fix. I'll write:

```java
static boolean mayBeString(Node n, boolean recurse) {
    if (recurse) {
      for (Node child = n.getFirstChild(); child != null; child = child.getNext()) {
        if (mayBeString(child, true)) {
          return true;
        }
      }
      return false;
    } else {
      return mayBeStringHelper(n);
    }
}
```

